{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "Wire 生成提醒",
  "description": "当 wire.go 文件被编辑时，提醒运行 wire 命令生成代码",
  "version": "1",
  "when": {
    "type": "fileEdited",
    "patterns": [
      "**/wire.go"
    ]
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "wire.go 文件已修改。请检查是否需要运行 `wire ./cmd/{service}/export` 或 `make generate` 来重新生成 wire_gen.go。如果依赖关系有变更，确保依赖顺序正确：基础设施 → Data 层 → Business 层 → Service 层。"
  }
}